OL,4,Cpublic opposition to elected mayors
OL,6,FThe first mayoral elections in
OL,7,FHampshire and Sussex are planned for
OL,8,FMay 2026, pending the approval of
OL,9,FParliament and some of the affected
OL,10,Flocal councils.
OL,12,FAn official public consultation found
OL,13,F62% of residents in Hampshire and the
OL,14,FIsle of Wight disagreed with the
OL,15,Fproposed new governance arrangements.
OL,16,FOut of 5,988 respondents, just 24%
OL,17,Fagreed with the proposals.
