OL,3,CConservative leader 'understands'
OL,4,Cpublic opposition to elected mayors
OL,6,FOpposition was even higher in Sussex,
OL,7,Fwith 66% of the 5,959 members of the
OL,8,Fpublic who responded to the
OL,9,Fconsultation disagreeing with the
OL,10,Fplans for a mayoral combined county
OL,11,Fauthority.
OL,13,FAsked by ITV News Meridian if she
OL,14,Funderstood local opposition to the new
OL,15,Fdirectly-elected mayors, Kemi Badenoch
OL,16,Fsaid: "Yes, I do understand it and
OL,17,FI've seen it all over the country.
