OL,3,CConservative leader 'understands'
OL,4,Cpublic opposition to elected mayors
OL,6,F"But Labour has decided that. We're
OL,7,Fnot in government anymore. The
OL,8,FConservatives are the opposition so we
OL,9,Fhave to make the best of it."
OL,11,FKemi Badenoch added: "The thing is,
OL,12,Fdevolution doesn't work if you get the
OL,13,Fwrong people in. Where devolution goes
OL,14,Fwrong, as we've seen with the SNP
OL,15,Frunning Scotland and Labour running
OL,16,FWales, is that when people don't have
OL,17,Fgood ideas, don't have the high
OL,18,Fcalibre of candidates then it will go
OL,19,Fwrong."
