OL,3,CConservative leader 'understands'
OL,4,Cpublic opposition to elected mayors
OL,6,FThe Tory leader visited Ryde alongside
OL,7,Fthe party's candidate for mayor of
OL,8,FHampshire and the Solent, Donna Jones,
OL,9,FIsle of Wight East MP, Joe Robertson,
OL,10,Fand Shadow Chancellor, Mel Stride.
OL,12,FThe Conservatives are the only major
OL,13,Fparty to select their candidates for
OL,14,Fthe new mayoral races in the South.
OL,15,FLong-serving police and crime
OL,16,Fcommissioner, Katy Bourne, is the
OL,17,Fparty's pick for the Sussex position.
